==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Steadiness
<hw>Stead"i*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
steady.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Steadiness</qex> is a point of prudence as well as of
courage.</q> <rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Constancy; resolution;
unchangeableness.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Steading</ent>⟦br⟧
